Steps to run the 488 Paint program:

1. Navigate to `cs488/handin/A0/src`
2. From this directory, run the makefile by typing `make` into the terminal
3. Now run the program by typing `./paint488`
4. Begin drawing on the canvas: the default shape is a black line
5. You can change the shape and colours of the paint program through the toolbar menus
6. You can quit the program by pressing 'Q', or clicking the Quit button
